messages.text: do you have a plan of action?
a plan of action based on what?
I’ll go to the wedding and see what I can do
if I follow her maybe we can find a moment alone and run to the car
I’ll do my best and if we can’t make it, well…
she’ll have to live with it
looks like the whole of Weeping Rock is here
there’s an altar at the far end of the room
I don’t know I can’t see her
everyone is just standing here in silence
I suppose they’re waiting for the bride and groom to arrive
I can see Nazarene. She’s standing in the crowd
she isn’t wearing her wedding dress or anything
she just gave me a very scared look
get the hell out of there
no, I want to understand what’s happening
oh wait Isaiah walked up to the altar
he says he must decrease, and a more rightful one must increase
I don’t know what he means
he just said: Sean, come forth!
why are you dressed like that?!
today is the happiest day of my life
I always knew this is what I really am
who gave birth to the son of God when she was about to be burned?
are you out of your mind?
and her son. The son of God. It’s me.
she ran away out of fear. She wasn’t faithful enough.
and they tested me to make sure I really was the son of God.
Sean, listen to me. I don’t believe there’s any god.
and even if there were you certainly wouldn’t be his son.
it’s official. I am the new leader. This is my home now.
I could feel something was wrong!
you don’t understand that they’ve brainwashed you!
just take a step back and think for a minute
I read your texts. Are you Sean’s brother?
what have you done to my brother?
you lured him into a trap
not willingly! My family tricked me
they know how rebellious I am.
They arranged this fake marriage just to make me want to escape
Father made sure I found Sean’s number and offered me a cell phone for my birthday
he said I’d have fun texting my sisters.
He knew what I would use it for
why are you using my brother’s phone now?
let me start from the top
and he decided to take a wife to celebrate
let me guess. He wanted you
they brought me to his room
he tried to take off my dress…
why are you texting me from his phone?
how hard did you hit him?
Nazarene, did you kill my brother?
I didn’t mean to kill hi
I want to see who I’m talking to
I know what kind of person my brother was becoming
you did what you had to do
the town will be awake in a couple of hours
as long as I stay in here they’ll think we’re sleeping
but I’ll have to come out at some point
there’s no crime worse than killing him
I can’t even imagine what they’ll do to punish me
you don’t have to be scared anymore
I’m on my way to Weeping Rock. I’ll be there very soon
I could tell my brother had lost his mind.
I knew something bad would happen.
of course. I’ll take you away
sneak out of the room now before anyone wakes up
will you go to the police?
no. I want to forget Weeping Rock ever existed
the security guard is making his rounds.
it should take about ten minutes
there’s something you should probably know
I’d rather say it through text than in person
you know how we were told your brother was the son of God?
yeah I know the story. And there’s something missing
Mother often told me that when he was younger my uncle Isaiah had a special relationship with Anna your mom...
even if she was very shy.
like she was his favourite. Mother never says things straight but…
he raped her. What an animal
did your mom know my mom well?
